_:Nab3ae10b9ef14e149f9cbd4c6c649910 <http://schema.org/name> "The Rt Hon Michael Tomlinson KC" .
_:Nab3ae10b9ef14e149f9cbd4c6c649910 <http://schema.org/image> <https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6571d4e5049516000d49be32/s465_minister.png> .
<https://www.gov.uk/> <http://schema.org/name> "Home" .
_:Nab3ae10b9ef14e149f9cbd4c6c649910 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Michael Tomlinson was Minister of State at the Home Office between 7 December 2023 and 5 July 2024.</p>\n\n<p>He was Solicitor General between 7 September 2022 and 7 December 2023.</p>\n\n<p>He was previously a Vice Chamberlain of HM Household (Government Whip) between 8 July 2022 and 7 September 2022, and Government Whip (Lord Commissioner of HM Treasury) between 14 February 2020 and 8 July 2022.</p>\n" .
